{"name":"King Kurtis","size":"medium","type":"humanoid","tag":"Snowchester, King","alignment":"Lawful Evil","hitDice":"16","armorName":"plate","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":3,"otherArmorDesc":"10","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"22 (5d8)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"20","dexPoints":"8","conPoints":"16","intPoints":"10","wisPoints":"12","chaPoints":"18","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"60","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"5","customCr":"1 (200 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The monster can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The monster regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the monster can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the monster can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The monster can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the monster's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the monster's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the monster dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Arctic Wind","desc":"[MON] slams his sword in the ground as the harsh, frigid snow surrounds the King of Snowchester. The movement speed of all creatures within a 10ft. radius of [MON] are quartered."}],"actions":[{"name":"Multiattack","desc":"[MON] makes two weapon attacks."},{"name":"Midas Sword","desc":"[MON] swings a beaming sword forged from pure gold. [STR ATK + 1] to hit. _Hit:_ [STR 2D6] slashing damage. [MON] may do 1 radiant damage for every 10 GP he expends (up to 200 GP and 20 radiant damage)."},{"name":"Gemstone Gauntlet","desc":"[MON] fires 4 explosive gemstones (minimum 50GP each) at creatures within 60ft. For each gemstone: [CHA ATK] to hit _Hit:_ [CHA 2D6] radiant damage. The gemstones are consumed."},{"name":"Pickaxe of Snowchester","desc":"[MON] mines up to three 5x5 blocks. [STR ATK + 1] to hit. _Hit:_ [STR 8D10 + 1] magical bludgeoning damage."}],"bonusActions":[{"name":"Construct","desc":"[MON] places up to six 5x5 blocks on unoccupied spaces within a 30ft. radius. These blocks do not deal damage."},{"name":"Royal Decree","desc":"[MON] makes a royal order. Until the end of their next turn, up to 3 allies gain the effect of haste (without the lethargy)."}],"reactions":[],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"str","order":0},{"name":"con","order":2}],"skills":[{"name":"athletics","stat":"str","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"insight","stat":"wis","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"intimidation","stat":"cha"},{"name":"perception","stat":"wis"}],"damagetypes":[],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"Kurtis","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":1,"damage":[]}